	<h1 class="title">麻省理工和这些艺术家联手，或许可以变成“当代达·芬奇”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Hilarie M. Sheets</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-16 12:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/23396/medium/23396.jpg?1457314242" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


